<navigation-bar title="首页" homeButton="{{true}}" background="#f3f5f7"></navigation-bar>

<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="page-body">
    <view class="page-hero">
      <text class="page-eyebrow">HOME SHELL</text>
      <text class="page-title">主包首页占位</text>
      <text class="page-subtitle">
        这里用于承接初始化后的主包壳层，后续再按业务需求继续扩展主包入口内容。
      </text>
    </view>

    <view class="page-card">
      <text class="section-title">运行上下文</text>
      <view class="info-grid">
        <view class="info-item">
          <text class="info-label">环境</text>
          <text class="info-value">{{envLabel}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="info-item">
          <text class="info-label">当前用户</text>
          <text class="info-value">{{displayName}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="info-item">
          <text class="info-label">角色</text>
          <text class="info-value">{{currentRole}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="info-item">
          <text class="info-label">未读消息</text>
          <text class="info-value">{{unreadCount}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="page-card">
      <text class="section-title">下一步入口</text>
      <view class="page-actions">
        <button class="page-button" bindtap="goWorkbench">进入工作台</button>
        <button class="page-button page-button--ghost" bindtap="logout">退出登录</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
